text.tspan: The Fumos have trapped you. You have to defend yourself until 6 AM.
Right click or tap anywhere in the room to use your camera flash. Your flash
can only reach two doors or vents at a time, so aim carefully.
Reimu and Marisa will come through the left and right doors respectively.
Use your flash to scare them away.
Keep the music box behind you wound up in order to stay sane. Watch out for
Yukari, though. Look at cam 12 to ensure she's not waiting for you at the music
